maine gandhi ko nahin ( english : silence of the king ) is a 2008 indian tamil drama film written and directed by anjan dutt . the film stars prashanth , aishwarya rai , aishwarya rai , aishwarya rai , aishwarya rai , aishwarya rai , kulbhushan kharbanda , and irrfan khan in the lead roles . the film is a remake of tamil film &lt;unk&gt; .